snippet.textDisplay:
The Punjabis that have moved to the Uk decades ago retain many of the older historical values of their parents generation.  We did forget our language but for many of us it was harder as we had to understand and work with English. 

The deterioration of our culture in the Punjab and elsewhere in India should be attributed to the influence of. Bollywood films and modern Indian dramas.  I’m glad that the next generation are valuing the punjabi language and culture.
